description: The island will remain at level two of its safe exit framework from lockdown for the rest of July.
title: Coronavirus: Jersey delays next phase of lockdown easing
title_page: Coronavirus: Jersey delays next phase of lockdown easing - BBC News
maintext: The panel - the Scientific and Technical Advisory Cell - is due to meet again on 3 August and if there are no significant changes in the low levels of Covid-19, it is likely to advise ministers to move to level one.
